- exclude packages [[http://spacemacs.org/doc/DOCUMENTATION.html#excluding-packages][doc]]
- 忽略某个layer中的package [[http://spacemacs.org/doc/DOCUMENTATION.html#selectingignoring-packages-of-a-layer][doc]]

